    dc:description "Fig. 54. Eoplinthicus yazooensis Cappetta & Stringer, 2002, median tooth. A–E.ALMNH PV1985.35.65, Gosport Sand. A. Lingual view. B. Labial view. C. Oral view. D. Basal view. E. Profile view. Labial at top in oral and basal views. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
